      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "1. From the previous chain from al-Hassan from al-Hussain b. Abi al-’Ala from Abi Abdillah (a.s.) who said: “One who recites Surah Bani Israel every Thursday night won’t die until he meets Qaim (a.t.f.s.) and becomes one of his companions.”"
